            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "[Arborist.nvim](https://github.com/arborist-ts/arborist.nvim) guy here. \n\nI started this as an experiment. I've been daily driving it. And daily bug fixing it. Anyway...\n\nI'm happy to hand over the Arborist org to anyone who wants to maintain it. \n\nAnd happy to deprecate it if the community chooses to consolidate around one direction. \n\nNo pride in owning it here. But glad to chip in as a community member. \n\nI just need a Treesitter manager I can install and the promptly forget about. ",
